%% 图6 消息流转时序图
sequenceDiagram
    participant U1 as 用户A
    participant LN1 as LeafNodeA
    participant Hub as Hub
    participant LN2 as LeafNodeB
    participant U2 as 用户B
    
    Note over U1,U2: 私聊消息发送流程
    
    U1->>U1: 获取好友公钥
    U1->>U1: NaCl Box加密
    U1->>U1: 本地SQLite保存
    
    U1->>LN1: Publish<br/>dchat.dm.xxx.msg
    LN1->>Hub: LeafNode转发
    
    Hub->>Hub: JetStream持久化
    Hub->>LN2: 路由消息
    
    LN2->>U2: 推送消息
    U2->>U2: NaCl Box解密
    U2->>U2: 本地SQLite保存
    U2->>U2: UI更新
    
    Note over Hub: 服务端仅中转密文<br/>无法解密内容
